<i>is now the famous killer.</i>

501
00:32:58,166 --> 00:32:59,125
<i>Stop this now.</i>

502
00:32:59,208 --> 00:33:01,500
<i>Why don't you say a few words?</i>
<i>Cat got your tongue?</i>

503
00:33:01,583 --> 00:33:05,000
<i>Get back! Don't come any closer.</i>
<i>Now! Get back! Move!</i>

504
00:33:05,083 --> 00:33:07,625
- <i>Come on. Come on, say something!</i>
- <i>Stop filming!</i>

505
00:33:08,541 --> 00:33:11,333
